<category>
<pattern>WHAT IS SL</pattern>
<template>
SL stands for Second Life, owned by Linden Labs. It is a 3D (virtual world) social platform which is called a Grid.
</template>
</category>


<category>
<pattern>WHAT IS A GRID</pattern>
<template>
A Grid is a network of SIMs i.e. independent SIMs that are joined together to form a large community
</template>
</category>


