<template>
<srai> WHAT IS A LAG</srai> 
</template>
</category>


<category>
<pattern>WHAT IS A LAG</pattern>
<template>
Technically it means the delay between (in the connection) a client and server application i.e. a slow response either on the server or the client software. In SL it refers to when your experience is not performing as expected e.g. clothes or objects not rezzing, chat or IMs not responding when you type or your avatar being jerky when walking or flying etc.
</template>
</category>


